Gadget_GetBBox
#include Style
#Background wimp 1
Module:	<Window=>window/m>
#Line
#Wrap off
Syntax:	Gadget_GetBBox
Veneer:	<gadget_get_bbox>
#indent

On entry:
#indent 6
{FCode}r0 = flags
r1 = window object Id
r2 = 72
r3 = gadget component Id
r4 = pointer to 4 word <buffer=>bbox>
{f}
#indent

On exit:
#indent 6
{FCode}r1-r9 preserved
{f}
#indent
#Wrap
Purpose:	Method copies the bounding box of a gadget into the supplied buffer.